<i>noun</i>: 침착 [침착], 냉정 [냉ː정] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>침착 [침착]</dt><br>
<dd>calmness; coolness; composure</dd><br>
<dd>쉽게 흥분하지 않고 행동이 조심스럽고 차분함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of acting carefully and calmly, not being excited easily.</dd><br>
<dt>냉정 [냉ː정]</dt><br>
<dd>coolness</dd><br>
<dd>생각이나 행동이 감정에 좌우되지 않고 침착함.</dd><br>
<dd>A composed attitude in which thoughts or behavior are not swayed by feelings.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>